subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Morgan Pressel birdied the final hole in the inaugural Kapalua L.P.G.A. Classic in Hawaii for her first victory of the season. The 20-year-old Pressel closed with a three-under-par 69 to edge Suzann Pettersen by a stroke.
